Third, particles exhibit wave-particle duality. They show

60
00:02:56,427 --> 00:02:59,563
wave-like behavior through interference and diffraction.

61
00:02:59,650 --> 00:03:03,732
Finally, there's the uncertainty principle. We cannot simultaneously know

62
00:03:03,832 --> 00:03:06,367
the exact position and momentum of a particle.

63
